{
  "texts": [
    "For example, AI-powered electronic noses have been integrated into smart refrigerators to detect food spoilage by analyzing volatile organic compounds, providing real-time alerts that help prevent food waste and improve household food safety (Shehzad 2025).",
    "In the beverage industry, companies are increasingly applying machine learning models to analyze sensory panel data and consumer feedback.",
    "These models can identify which combinations of taste, aroma, and texture are most preferred by different demographic groups (Ayoub et al. 2025).",
    "This enables manufacturers to develop or reformulate products to better match consumer expectations.",
    "Moreover, firms such as Givaudan and Nuritas are leveraging AI to identify bioactive peptides and functional ingredients that influence taste perception and mouthfeel."
  ]
}